FUNCTION LFACRELA
=MEN_LIN("ESPERE POR FAVOR")
=WORKING()
=DOTALK()
SELE FAC
SET ORDE TO TAG FACTURA
SET ORDE TO TAG CODCLI IN PER
SET RELA TO FAC.CODCLI INTO PER
SET ORDE TO TAG CODVIA IN VIA
SET RELA TO FAC.CODVIA INTO VIA ADDI
SET ORDE TO TAG PAGCOD IN MIX
SET RELA TO FAC.CONDPAGO INTO MIX ADDI
SELE FAX
